last_episode_to_air.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle set out to take away Fearless Leader’s super powers and save the world.

name: The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle
original_name: The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle
overview: The world-famous talking moose and flying squirrel are back in The Adventures of Rocky and Bullwinkle, a comedy about two goofball friends who end up in harrowing situations but end up saving the day time and again. As their silly ambitions dovetail with Fearless Leader's sinister plans to take over the world, they are set on a collision course with his notorious super spies Boris and Natasha.

episodes.name: The Stink of Fear: Chapter One
episodes.overview: When Rocky and Bullwinkle travel to Paris to enter a cooking competition, Fearless Leader sends super spies Boris and Natasha after Bullwinkle to steal his secret recipe.

episodes.name: The Stink of Fear: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: While Boris and Natasha continue their mission and Bullwinkle tries to overcome his stage-fright to advance in the cooking competition, a secret government agency begins tracking Rocky & Bullwinkle's movements

episodes.name: The Stink of Fear: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: When Bullwinkle remembers he forgot the secret ingredient to his stinky pie recipe, he and Rocky travel to Norway and enlist the help of his beloved Grandwinkle, not knowing that they are being followed!

episodes.name: The Stink of Fear: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: Director Peachfuzz recruits Rocky and Bullwinkle to help her infiltrate Fearless Leader's hideout, and Boris and Natasha are replaced by a robot henchman.

episodes.name: The Stink of Fear: Chapter Five
episodes.overview: When Fearless Leader brainwashes Bullwinkle, Rocky must team up with Director Peachfuzz to stop them from making the stinky pie and taking over the world.

episodes.name: Dark Side of the Moose: Chapter One
episodes.overview: When Rocky and Bullwinkle want an interesting story to tell at their upcoming reunion, they accidentally take off for space in a very real rocket.

episodes.name: Dark Side of the Moose: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle encounter a young alien and set out on a mission to reunite him with his alien family but things get complicated when they accidentally lose him at an alien convention and Boris, Natasha and other eccentric billionaire Colonel Boudreaux are also after him.

episodes.name: Dark Side of the Moose: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: A super-powered Rocky almost defeats Fearless Leader, but accidentally overdoes it, driving Fearless Leader to take his powers into space for the ultimate space take-over-the-world evil plan.

episodes.name: Dark Side of the Moose: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: Bullwinkle reunites Cloyd with his parents who then take him to outer space to stop Fearless Leader and rescue Rocky.

episodes.name: Moosebumps!: Chapter One
episodes.overview: Eager to come face-to-face with a real life monster, Rocky and Bullwinkle buy a creepy old mansion in hopes of finding a real monster.

episodes.name: Moosebumps!: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: After Bullwinkle drinks a monster serum, he can't control when he turns into a big hairy monster, so he and Rocky go on the run from angry mobs and internet celebrities.

episodes.name: Moosebumps!: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: Bullwinkle and Rocky fly to a mysterious monster-inhabited island to meet the missing mad scientist that created the serum that turned Bullwinkle into a monster, only to learn of the biggest, meanest monster on the island, Humongalon.

episodes.name: Moosebumps!: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: When Fearless Leader uses the monster Humongalon to force everyone to surrender the world to him, Rocky and Bullwinkle try to stop them in the most massive monster battle ever.

episodes.name: Almost Famoose: Chapter One
episodes.overview: When Rocky and Bullwinkle damage the largest birdbath in the world, they set out on a musical adventure. And Fearless Leader attempts to become a musical superstar so he can amass a legion of devoted super fans who will obey his every command.

episodes.name: Almost Famoose: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: A video of Rocky and Bullwinkle playing a song goes viral and they’re rocketed to musical superstardom. They decide to use their newfound celebrity to launch a “save the birdbath” concert tour to restore the giant birdbath they destroyed.

episodes.name: Almost Famoose: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: Rocky, Bullwinkle, Boris and Natasha are kidnapped by a super-fan named Francis, the eight-year-old heir to the Puffy Platypus Pizza franchise, to play a private concert for his birthday.

episodes.name: Almost Famoose: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle return to Frostbite Falls to discover that because they failed to rebuild the giant birdbath, their beloved town is now completely overrun with dirty, zombie-like birds.

episodes.name: The Legends of the Power Gems: Chapter One
episodes.overview: While celebrating their friend-iversary at their favorite restaurant, Long Tom Lobster’s, Rocky and Bullwinkle solve a seemingly impossible maze on the kids’ menu.

episodes.name: The Legends of the Power Gems: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: On a quest to find the power gem of fire, Rocky and Bullwinkle travel to Hawaii and enter a surf contest to get the gem back.

episodes.name: The Legends of the Power Gems: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle battle one more guardian to get the final power gem – the wind gem.

episodes.name: The Legends of the Power Gems: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: With all three elemental power gems in hand, Fearless Leader sets out to take over the world, but Rocky and Bullwinkle save the world!

episodes.name: Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder: Chapter One
episodes.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle create superhero alter egos Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder and set out on an adventure to save Frostbite Frannie – and summer vacation!

episodes.name: Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder: Chapter Two
episodes.overview: When a mysterious goop gives Fearless Leader real life superpowers, Rocky and Bullwinkle must reprise their masked hero personas to take on super powered “Fearless Laser” and stop him from lasering his face on the moon!

episodes.name: Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder: Chapter Three
episodes.overview: The mystery goop strikes again when Rocky’s stress ball falls into a vat of goop, making it sentient and gigantic! Rocky and Bullwinkle use the goop to give super powers to themselves to try and stop the ball, but when they fail, they recruit the actor that plays their favorite TV hero, Captain Great Guy, and give him goop super powers as well.

episodes.name: Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder: Chapter Four
episodes.overview: In an attempt to reverse Fearless Leader's goop-induced evil powers, Rocky and Bullwinkle travel to an alternate reality to get an "anti-goop."

episodes.name: Amazamoose and Squirrel Wonder: Chapter Five
episodes.overview: Rocky and Bullwinkle set out to take away Fearless Leader’s super powers and save the world.
